  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>A Jetpack trail emitting the light of living stone; plucked from a slumbering guardian; focused and consolidated through a series of lenses.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>喷气背包的尾迹散发着活石的光芒；取自沉睡的守护者；经由一整组透镜聚焦凝练。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>從沉睡的守護者身上摘下活石頭，經過一系列鏡頭聚焦和加固，噴射背包的尾跡才能散發如此光芒。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
